with each attack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1168870/extras/d9a0d1f2453af2edc85bbf9745676192.avif?t=1653368212\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiplayer Co-op<br></li><li>Five Playable Heroes<br></li><li>Leveling<br></li><li>Quests<br></li><li>Talents<br></li><li>Familiars<br></li><li>10+ Biomes<br></li><li>Day and Night cycle<br></li><li>Dungeons [Normal, Heroic, Mythic+]<br></li><li>Lootable Skills [Proc System]<br></li><li>Lots of Equipment Status Variation [Affix & Suffix System]<br></li><li>Corruption System<br></li><li>Relics<br></li><li>Perks<br></li><li>Crafting [Blacksmith, Cooking, Alchemy]<br></li><li>Farming<br></li><li>Building<br></li><li>Enchanting<br></li><li>Reforge & Refine<br></li><li>Tower Defense every 7 days<br></li><li>Events<br></li><li>Gathering Resources [Mining, Fishing, Lumber, Herboism]<br></li><li>Achievements<br></li><li>Rare Monsters with rare loots<br></li><li>Bosses</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1168870/extras/9ba16795f335319dea554679c556d292.poster.avif?t=1653368212\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1168870/extras/9ba16795f335319dea554679c556d292.webm?t=1653368212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1168870/extras/9ba16795f335319dea554679c556d292.mp4?t=1653368212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
